@deray This was my only symptom as well (along with a mild sore throat) and I also tested positive. I'm beyond thankful I was able to get tested and never got sicker. I hope you have a speedy recovery as well.

Since then, I have known two other people ages 52 and 75 yo who had this as their only symptom and also tested positive. They are married and I had no contact with either of them. I do think it’s interesting that we are all in different age brackets and all had same outcome.
